<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section id="faq" class="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-center">Frequently <span class="text-blue">Asked Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subheading">Got questions? We've got answers. If you don't see what you're looking for, just reach out to our team.</p>
        
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">How does <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> help reduce waiting times?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Smart Queue uses advanced algorithms to optimize customer flow and service allocation. Customers can join the queue remotely and receive real-time updates about their position and expected wait time. This allows them to arrive just in time for their service, eliminating the need to physically wait in line. For businesses, our analytics dashboard helps identify bottlenecks and optimize staffing to further reduce waiting times.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">Can customers join the queue remotely?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Absolutely! Customers can join the queue through multiple channels: our mobile app, website, SMS, or on-site kiosk. Once in the queue, they'll receive updates and can track their position from anywhere, allowing them to make better use of their time instead of standing in a physical line.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">What industries can benefit from <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span>?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Smart Queue is highly versatile and works for almost any business that deals with customer waiting. Our system is currently used in retail stores, restaurants, healthcare facilities, government offices, banks, educational institutions, and service centers. The platform is customizable to fit the specific needs of different industries.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">How difficult is it to implement <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> in my business?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Implementation is straightforward and can typically be completed within 1-2 days. Our system is designed to be user-friendly with minimal hardware requirements—often just a tablet or computer for staff and optional display screens or kiosks. Our team provides comprehensive onboarding and training to ensure a smooth transition.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">Can <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> integrate with our existing systems?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! Smart Queue offers robust API integration capabilities that allow it to connect with your CRM, POS, appointment scheduling software, and other business systems. This ensures a seamless flow of information across your technology stack. Our integration specialists will work with you to set up these connections.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">What kind of analytics does <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> provide?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Our analytics dashboard gives you valuable insights into your operations, including average wait times, service duration, peak hours, customer flow, and staff performance. These metrics help you make data-driven decisions to optimize your operations, improve resource allocation, and enhance the customer experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">Is <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> suitable for businesses of all sizes?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Absolutely! Smart Queue is designed to scale with your business. We offer different plans tailored to businesses of all sizes, from small local shops to large enterprises with multiple locations. The system can handle anything from 10 to 10,000+ customers per day across single or multiple locations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span class="question-text">How secure is the <span class="text-blue">Smart Queue</span> system?</span>
                    <span class="toggle-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Security is a top priority for us. Smart Queue uses enterprise-grade encryption for all data, both in transit and at rest. We're compliant with GDPR and other relevant data protection regulations. We implement strict access controls and regular security audits to ensure your data and your customers' information remains safe.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    
